children.description: Verify children as Button, TextEntry or hr element

flyoutPlacement.description: Specifically used with flyout, identifies what side the flyout is on

stretch.description: Stretches the width of the container

id.description: Id applied to the input, used for the for attribute on the label

label.description: Optional label to float above input, placeholder will not show when using this

placeholder.description: Placeholder for the input, do not supply with a floating label

resize.description: Allows a multiline input to be resized

required.description: Add asterik to supplied label, aria-required

size.description: Set the size of the input

suggestion.description: Text to suggest as completion of the input

ariaLabels.description: Sets aria labels for the internals

button.description: Sets a button within the input

clearable.description: Determines if a clear button should be included

items.description: List of possible results to show in flyout

onConfirm.description: Callback when an item is selected within the results flyout or enter key press in the search box. The first argument is the id of the item.

onSelect.description: Callback when an item is selected within the results flyout. The first argument is the id of the item.

open.description: If content is set within the list, this controls visibility
